column3: Sand Dollars are a favorite find for the avid Beachcomber! Our Sand Dollars are made from reclaimed wood. They are individually hand-painted and distressed to give them a salty, aged look. Small cracks, knots and imperfections are all part of the allure! A perfect accent for any coastal home. Note: Two othere sizes available. Group together in three sizes for a unique statement wall! Each has a sawtooth hook for simple hanging.

column1: Product Detail - Seahorse Wood - Large - Aqua
column3:
Seahorses are beautiful, fascinating and mysterious! Images of these sea dwellers are found in coastal homes the world over.

Our Seashorses are made from reclaimed wood. Each is hand-painted and distressed to give them a salty, aged look. Small cracks, knots and imperfections are all part of the allure!

Note: These come in 2 sizes and three colors. Grouping together adds to the charm!

Each has a sawtooth hook for simple hanging.
